::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe's charred body flies backwards out of the cave as the shots hit 
him, blowing him through several trees. He falls to the ground, barely 
muttering "Beast Mode" as he transforms to his beast mode.

He barely activates the jetpacks on his sides, flying off. He had not 
expected that. Any sensible leader would apreciate more bots to follow him. 
DeathStorm shruggs as his internal repairs activate again. He'd just go to 
another faction....
